{
  "texts": [
    "For the O6BG cotreatment experiments, LN18 cells were pretreated with 100 μM O6BG 3 h before the first treatment 20 µM O6BG + TMZ.",
    "To visualize colonies, culture plates were stained with 0.05% crystal violet in 1× PBS containing 1% methanol and 1% formaldehyde ~12 days after cell seeding.",
    "The plates were scanned using an Epson perfection V800 scanner set to \"positive film\" mode.",
    "Smart-seq2 single-cell RNA-seq data generated using malignant GBM cells were obtained from GSM3828672 45.",
    "Data normalization and preprocessing were performed using the Seurat workflow 76."
  ]
}